lyrics:
[Verse]
Ric walked in that office, with a heart full of hope
Met his client at FWD insurance, it was hard to cope
The lack of organization, got him feeling low
Now he's frustrated, lost in the unknown

[Chorus]
Oh Ric, don't let it bring you down
Keep fighting, turn that frown around
Hold on tight, don't let them steal your glow
Ric, show 'em what you know
